---
title: Bacon, Mushroom & Sage Risotto with Pear Salad
description: Risotto is so delicious, but the prospect of all that stirring can sometimes be a bit daunting! Our version lets you put your risotto
in the oven and forget about it until it's time to eat. All the creamy, luxurious texture with none of the elbow work!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/bacon-mushroom-sage-risotto-2b25b97c.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/bacon-mushroom-sage-risotto-611f3fbd3112b2503435cc33-550af724.pdf
cuisine: Italian
servings: 2
course: main course
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/bacon-mushroom-and-sage-risotto-611f3fbd3112b2503435cc33
